        <abstract> 
<p>Praises AG’s abstract of <hi rend="italic">Cross and self-fertilisation</hi> [<hi rend="italic">Am. J. Sci.</hi> 3d ser. 13 (1877): 125–41].</p> 
            <p>Hopes soon to finish with dimorphic plants.</p>
